{"an8.18:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 8.18 ","an8.18:0.2":"2. Mahavagga ","an8.18:0.3":"Dutiyabandhanasutta ","an8.18:1.1":"“Atthahi, bhikkhave, akarehi puriso itthim bandhati. ","an8.18:1.2":"Katamehi atthahi? ","an8.18:1.3":"Runnena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati; ","an8.18:1.4":"hasitena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati; ","an8.18:1.5":"bhanitena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati; ","an8.18:1.6":"akappena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati; ","an8.18:1.7":"vanabhangena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati; ","an8.18:1.8":"gandhena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati; ","an8.18:1.9":"rasena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati; ","an8.18:1.10":"phassena, bhikkhave, puriso itthim bandhati. ","an8.18:1.11":"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, atthahakarehi puriso itthim bandhati. ","an8.18:1.12":"Te, bhikkhave, satta subaddha, ye phassena baddha”ti. ","an8.18:1.13":"Atthamam. "}